        "html": "<p>Montrer qu’il existe un unique polyn<span>ô</span>me <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(P_n \\in { K[X]}\\)</span> tel que <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(P_n(X) + P_n(X+1) = 2X^n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "551c9aec-c5ee-49fe-be50-15637c9e8756",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Isomorphisme $P \\longmapsto P(X) + P(X+1)$.",
        "html": "<p>Isomorphisme <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P \\longmapsto P(X) +\nP(X+1)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
